beer_brewer_name: Radomyshl Beer and Beverage Plant (Oasis Beverages)
review_blob: Best Ukrainian wheat beer. Genuine taste. Colour and head are fantastic. Reminds me about Germany.
Excellent porter with brilliant aftertaste. Be sure to buy one that bottled in St. Petersburg.
Nice lager, but taste largely varies from barrel to barrel. Sometimes the taste is excellent (especially from tap), sometimes  its very plain.
Not a beer at all. Perfumed and muddy crap. Quite popular, however, for its "unusual" taste.
